# Shared constants (non-URL)

Route URLs live in `shared/constants/app-urls.ts` — see `app-urls.mdc`. This file covers other shared constant modules.

## BiH municipalities (`bih-cities.ts`)

| Export | Type | Use |
|--------|------|-----|
| `BIH_CITIES` | `readonly string[]` | Sorted municipality names (`localeCompare` with `bs`) |
| `BIH_CITY_OPTIONS` | `SelectOption[]` | `{ value: city, label: city }` — for form `autocomplete` / `select` fields |

- Path: `shared/constants/bih-cities.ts`
- Full list of BiH municipalities (FBiH, RS, Brčko) — **do not** duplicate city lists in feature files.
- Import: `import { BIH_CITY_OPTIONS } from '…/shared/constants/bih-cities';`

**Current consumers:** `portal/user/features/routes/form/route.form.ts` (origin, destination), `portal/user/features/cargo/form/cargo.form.ts` (origin, destination).

```typescript
{
  key: 'origin',
  type: 'autocomplete',
  labelKey: '…fields.origin',
  options: BIH_CITY_OPTIONS,
}
```

City values are stored as plain strings (municipality name). No i18n per city — labels match stored values.

## User entity status (interim)

| Export | Type | Use |
|--------|------|-----|
| `UserEntityStatus` | union | `'open' \| 'in_progress' \| 'canceled' \| 'closed'` |
| `USER_ENTITY_STATUS_LABEL_KEYS` | `Record<UserEntityStatus, string>` | Maps to `shared.entityStatus.*` i18n keys |

- Path: `shared/constants/user-entity-status.ts`
- **Current consumers:** user `Route`, `Cargo`, `Storage` entity models; `StatusBadgeComponent`
- **Future:** each entity defines its own status union (e.g. `VehicleStatus`, `WarehouseStatus`) and label keys under `portal.<portal>.features.<entity>.status.*`. Keep `StatusBadgeComponent` + `--status-*` tokens as the shared display layer — see `entity-status.mdc`.

## Portal page icons

Entity icons for **sidebar section headers**, **collapsed flyout triggers**, and **`PageTitleComponent`**.

| File | Export | Keys |
|------|--------|------|
| `portal/admin/admin-page-icons.ts` | `AdminPageIcons` | `dashboard`, `users`, `vehicles`, `warehouses`, `settings` |
| `portal/user/user-page-icons.ts` | `UserPageIcons` | `dashboard`, `routes`, `cargo`, `storage` |

- `NavSection.icon` in nav configs — section title (expanded) + flyout trigger (collapsed desktop).
- Sidebar **items** are text-only (no per-link icons).
- Portal pages set `pageIcon` from `UserPageIcons` / `AdminPageIcons` — see `page-title.mdc`.
- **Do not** use `LucideSquarePlus` on page titles.

## Adding new shared constants

- **Geographic / domain lists** reused by 2+ features → `shared/constants/<name>.ts`, export typed options compatible with `SelectOption`.
- **Portal-only icons** → add to `admin-page-icons.ts` or `user-page-icons.ts`, then wire nav + pages.
- **Feature-specific enums** (cargo type, vehicle kind) → stay in feature `*.constants.ts`.

Related: `forms.mdc` (autocomplete + options), `page-title.mdc`, `app-urls.mdc`
